plot: Feeling confident in his new abilities, Mark risks a team-up with a local villain to take down a crime lord, while simultaneously juggling school and a new relationship.

invincible teams up with a minor-league enforcer villain, Titan, to take down Titan's boss Machine Head. But Machine Head has super-powered henchmen of his own, who defeat Invincible, Titan, and the Guardians when they come to Invincible's aid. Meanwhile, Amber gives Mark one last chance to be on time for their "date", and ends up bonding with Eve.—Gislef
